        </div>
        <div class="services-tagline">
            <p>From concept to completion, Build & Beyond offers comprehensive, tech-driven construction and design services tailored to your vision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-container">
            <div class="service-card" style="--order:1">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Residential Construction">
